Sony Says Outages, Building Damage May Have Occured at Plants After Quake

-- B y   M a r i k o   Y a s u
-- 
2011-03-11T07:44:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-11/sony-says-outages-building-damage-may-have-occured-at-plants.html
  Sony Corp. (6758) ’s factories in the
Tohoku region, northeastern Japan, may have incurred power
outages and damages to buildings, said Shinji Obana, a spokesman
in Tokyo. The company is assessing damages at the six plants, he
said.  The company makes Blu-ray discs, magnetic heads and
batteries in Tohoku, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
